Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:05.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HD9D9D9&\fs24\pos(378.86,526)}Brought to you by: Orange-Flash | Ko-Fi.com/OrangeFlash
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There! He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! Watch out! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Do not worry", you say? Ah, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no need to be so astonished over something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hattori Kanzou, a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kenichi, I'm... err. mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But how'd you get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From this window right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, from window. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you are a theif?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down, Ken'ichi-uji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A Ninja? Like those guys in a TV program?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A real Ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Who're you talking with?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But there isn't anyone except you in this room, Ken-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's right her-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd he gone to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of playing and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was really here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the TV program, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to bed already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you shouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cockroach?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, if you don't return home, your parents will get worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy, Hattori-kun says he is from in Iga province.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Inagaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him stay overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to return home now. I'll prepare the bed for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't need a bed", he says
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sleep on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm comfortable here, just the way I am..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's tired sleeping on the ceiling, so he's sleeping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,1.. 2.. 3.. 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels great to wake up early, once in a while. Today's gonna be a great day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, why did you mop the floor, so much that it slips?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When I woke up, the floor was sparkingly clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also the breakfast is also ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And even our laundry are washed thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But who possibly could have...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, I've figured out who did everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0} did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0} did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But who is this Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A Ninja from Iga village, Hattori Kanzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Kanzou-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, I don't want a stranger to spend night in our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You should talk. You should have told me yesterday night only.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I had headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Water is dripping from ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's sunny outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy is Hattori Kanzou?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cleaning the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for catching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to inform the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! He just came here yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hattori-kun's parents will be worried dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't inform the cops. It's their day off. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it'll be okay for him to stay in our home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna take a nap on ceiling again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm not used to sleeping on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep with my eyes up, if you sleep on the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you hang a futon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! I'm relieved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The wet futon looks like cross-shaped shuriken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected that a Ninja would wet his bed....